{"tid":28421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【電騙停不了】24歲女中招 被呃26萬人仔","createTime":"2016-12-08T02:31:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T02:35:21.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8c428d7eb2f5a5f7b3829cf65e2afe66e0748d13","tid":28421,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:31:32.000Z","msg":"Again Again <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n青衣牙鷹洲街8號灝景灣，一名24歲姓李女子昨晚報案，聲稱於11月接獲一名陌生男子來電，對方自稱為執法機關人員，表示報案人涉及一宗刑事案件，要求她於內地開設一個銀行戶口，並存入款項。<br />\n<br />\n女事主其後分多次匯款至該戶口。其後，報案人發現其戶口內共約26萬元人民幣的存款被人提走，懷疑受騙，於是報案。案件列作以欺騙手段取得財產，交由葵青警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56018455&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161208\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56018455%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161208&d=7zzUWbBCWXR1ISRxLjE2bJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=8fc5d037\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56018455%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161208&h=f3629150\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56018455&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161208</a>"},{"pid":"2fe8108a6235bbd5424c49b85b272fa0a181b8b9","tid":28421,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:33:20.000Z","msg":"仲中計果d只有兩個可能<br />\n一係豬咁蠢<br />\n一係身有屎"},{"pid":"f70038c3476d3ab5f36006f4ff38552253322e3f","tid":28421,"uid":12362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:35:21.000Z","msg":"咁輕易就比廿幾萬出去，佢應該都唔志在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}